": \"The Independent\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice Simone Bilesshould have little left to prove.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone Bilesshould\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Themost decorated gymnast in history, the American already has a haul of 37 World and Olympic medals in her collection, 27 of them glittering gold.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999197800989311, \"rank\": 7.91530746869337e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Themost\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnast\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"a haul\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"37 World and Olympic medals\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"her collection\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For nearly a decade, the 27-year-old has been the standout figure in her sport, her name and reputation evidence of excellence, Biles cutting through culturally as one of the world'smost popular and prominent athletes.\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly a decade\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"the standout figure\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"her sport\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"reputation evidence\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"the world'smost popular and prominent athletes\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Biles will head to her thirdOlympicsatParis 2024with a few bad memories to banish.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 872}, {\"ngram\": \"her thirdOlympicsatParis\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"a few bad memories\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a remarkable debut in Rio brought four gold medals to establish herself asgymnastics' ruling queen, her career nearly came crashing down entirely in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999800277217182, \"rank\": 1.9972677282413056e-05, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.765125965938587, \"rank\": 0.3069743037322676, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a remarkable debut\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"four gold medals\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"herself asgymnastics' ruling queen\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The problems began on her opening day of competition.\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1182, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The problems\", \"from\": 1129, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"her opening day\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Performing the all-around during qualification, Biles made a number of uncharacteristic errors, almost coming a cropper onboth the vault and the balance beam.Such is her ability that the Texan still managed to make all of the individual finals but something was clearly wrong.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1229}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1250}, {\"ngram\": \"uncharacteristic errors\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"a cropper onboth\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the vault\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"her ability\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"the Texan\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual finals\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On social media, Biles suggested that she was feeling \\\"the weight of the world on [her] shoulders\\\" - and worse was yet to come.The infamous 'twisties'(a temporary loss of air awareness) left Biles unable to complete her rotations, forcing her to withdraw from several events.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1736, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1539}, {\"ngram\": \"[her] shoulders\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1558}, {\"ngram\": \"The infamous 'twisties'(a temporary loss\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"air awareness\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"her rotations\", \"from\": 1677, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having overcome her mental block, Biles returned forbattle on the balance beam,nabbing a second medal to go along with team silver.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mental block\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"forbattle\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"a second medal\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"team silver\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was another two years before she would be seen in competition again.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another two years\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I say put mental health first,\\\" Biles said of her decision to step away in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2022, \"end\": 2027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.765125965938587, \"rank\": 0.3069743037322676, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1984}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because if you do not, then you are not going to enjoy your sport and you are not going to succeed as much as you want to.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sport\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's OK sometimes to even sit out the big competitions to focus on yourself, because it shows how strong of a competitor and person that you really are - rather than just battle through it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2153, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the big competitions\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"person\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not just in the arena that Biles has had battles to overcome.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"battles\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, the gymnast revealed that she hadbeen sexually abused by Larry Nassar,the disgraced former team doctor of the US Gymnastics team.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9999997290624746, \"rank\": 2.709377822209101e-07, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}, {\"begin\": 2538, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9919292700810133, \"rank\": 0.008129947497872296, \"text\": \"Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artistic_gymnastics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gymnast\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"the disgraced former team doctor\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nassar is serving between 40 and 175 years in prison for sexually abusing young female athletes in his care, with Biles among those testifying at the Senate in 2021 about how the system had failed to protect her.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2555, \"end\": 2561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8685438261344812e-36, \"text\": \"Nassar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2159907\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larry_Nassar\"}, {\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"score\": 0.5466530027357716, \"rank\": 0.6209569274531246, \"text\": \"Senate\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Senate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"between 40 and 175 years\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"prison\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2607}, {\"ngram\": \"sexually abusing young female athletes\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"his care\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After attending regular therapy, Biles at last felt ready to make her comeback last August.\", \"from\": 2769, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"regular therapy\", \"from\": 2785, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 2802, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"her comeback\", \"from\": 2835, \"to\": 2847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anticipation abounded as she stepped back into elite gymnastics atthe US Classic in Chicago.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2931, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.8996592006577326, \"rank\": 0.11129163370893998, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2945, \"end\": 2952, \"title\": \"http://